.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, march, january, november, december
There 5 different types of food: onion, artichoke, asparagus, nectarine, eggplant
The people have 5 different jobs:  social-worker, writer, mechanic, analyst, nurse
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, basketball, badminton, snowboarding

1. the person eating onion is the person who's birthday is in july
2. the person eating artichoke is the person who's sport is climbing
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who's birthday is in march
4. the person eating asparagus is the person drinking tea
5. the person who's birthday is in march is to the right of the person who's birthday is in january
6. the social-worker is the person who's sport is snowboarding
7. the writer is the person who's birthday is in november
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person eating nectarine is on the far left
10. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing
11. the writer is to the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton
12. the analyst is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the person eating eggplant is the nurse
14. the person eating nectarine is to the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Food	|   nectarine	|    asparagus	|     onion	|    artichoke	|    eggplant	|
| Birthday		|    november	|      december	|      july	|     january	|     march	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Job		|     writer	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| analyst	|   parliament	|
| Sport		|     sailing	|     badminton	|     snowboarding	|     climbing	|     basketball	|
